data.description: This 2 bedroom bungalow is conveniently located to all the amenities in town, yet, located on a quiet street. This home features hardwood floors, tall ceilings, an updated kitchen that offers plenty of  storage and a gas range. The primary bedroom has a custom organizer that can be used for a closet or your own personal library. You will have plenty of room to entertain with the option of two living areas or a formal dining area. There is an enclosed front porch and additional parking in the back of the home off the alley. Call today to schedule a private showing.
